            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>chicken</strong>&nbsp;into thin strips and coat them thoroughly in the <strong>cornflour</strong></p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan with a large drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;hot, add the <strong>chicken</strong> and cook for 2 min on each side, or until browned</p>\r\n<p>Once browned, transfer the chicken&nbsp;to a plate and keep the pan for the next step</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/273.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
